<p>The Long form pattern is designed to be used repetitively with a variety of
options to achieve an engaging, story-telling experience that still remains
consistent in look and feel. It's ideally suited to blend longer passages of 
text with images, video and audio. It also carries several sub-patterns.</p>

<h2>Usage</h2>

<ul>
	<li>Use a university header and university footer (an abbreviated footer 
        is typically acceptable).</li>
    <li>Use as many Long form sections as you want in between.</li>
    <li>The last Long form section should be a Credits variant, see below</li>
</ul>

